Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我本想交结曹操这个袅雄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁知弄巧成拙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}惹下了滔天巨祸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天哪 徐州难保了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲 曹老太爷之死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}罪在贼将张铠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲也只是用人不明而已呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:02:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿子琢磨着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一者我立刻派兵追杀张铠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}务必取他首级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二者由我携张铠的首级去趟兖州
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}面向曹操 向他说明事情的原委
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赔礼请罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们不正缺少粮饷么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们可以再赔偿他们几十万饷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}化解此事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你听说过一句话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宁肯我负天下人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}休叫天下人负我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这话谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你现在知道他是何等人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿啊 徐州大难临头了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲 那我们该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么办啊父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即刻传命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各部召集所有兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回防徐州 准备迎敌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等 我还有一事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操要是倾巢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仅凭我们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是难以阻挡曹操的大军哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我即刻写几道手书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你拿上它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}星夜兼程 去冀州拜见袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}南阳的袁术 平原的公孙瓒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们距离徐州都不过五日的行程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请他们发兵相救
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可说过 这几位诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可都贪图咱们徐州城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正因为他们贪图徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:05:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不愿意徐州落到曹操的手里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一旦落入曹操的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他便能称霸中原
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对他们尤为不利呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁能劝退曹操退兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}化干戈为玉帛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我陶谦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愿意每年向他们敬送
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二十万粮饷 至死不渝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可恨 可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}事已至此 请主公节哀自重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公下令 末将只需三千精兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五日之内便能踏平五凤山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将保证生擒张铠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿他脑袋来给曹老太爷祭灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 为何要征剿五凤山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杀害曹公的虽然是贼人张铠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:05:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是罪魁祸首
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却是那徐州城里的陶谦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公遭此大难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经是肝肠痛断
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}列位可否先退下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让主公稍作休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走吧 快走吧 走走走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下一者为主公悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二者 给主公道喜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧 你胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}家父刚刚过世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我何喜之有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}福中有祸 祸中有福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}福祸相倚 大事可期
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你所说的祸中之福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}指的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公心如明镜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何必要考问在下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公自起兵两年以来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}势如破竹 威震四方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但却有一桩难言之隐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就是虽然拥兵二十余万
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却只能蛰伏于兖州一隅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公要想成天下大业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}首先要图霸中原
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}中原首望之地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当数徐州六郡 因此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公心里头早就惦记着徐州了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否则的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公刚才的痛哭声中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么会带有这么凛然的杀机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让你说着了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就是想让他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把我的悲伤之情传出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传给天下的诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦杀了我爹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我痛不欲生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个消息已经顺风传出百里开外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是主公啊 徐州并不好取
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}继续说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下以为 取徐州有两难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这第一难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州刺史陶谦乃先帝钦命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此人治政以宽仁为本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}驭民以厚道著称
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}官声的口碑嘛也堪称上佳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因此 取之不义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这第二难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是冀州的袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}南阳的袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}平原的公孙瓒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}甚至连荆州的刘表
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都对徐州是垂涎三尺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们只是望而止步 探而不取
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是怕触犯众怒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}树敌于各路诸侯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们能听凭主公你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去取徐州吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你说我是取呢 还是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不取
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦命部下杀害主公父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此仇不报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天理难容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此外 陶谦厚道近乎迂腐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宽仁如同昏昧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像这样的人他能据配有徐州嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州是乃中原重镇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}扼黄河而望泰山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得之可纵横南北
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}苍天送徐州给主公
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如同送一杆大旗给狂风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}送一把宝剑给剑鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公不取何待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧 听你讲话如饮美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令人陶醉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}简直是一种享受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 在下建议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公即刻上疏朝廷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奏明陶谦之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并派人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到袁绍 袁术 公孙瓒处去报丧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让各路诸侯都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦杀害了主公父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此讯一到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们也就都明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公起兵去讨贼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是奉旨讨贼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上合天意 下合人情 中合道义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为此 这徐州非主公莫属了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我嘛 因为悲伤过度 不能执笔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就劳你代拟一道哀疏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在上奏朝廷的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}飞马传送给各路诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}表明杀父之仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和被迫起兵报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此疏在下已拟好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公过目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不必了 你写的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定是字字句句皆合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传命三军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日辰时起兵讨伐陶谦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊 此次出征
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你为什么不分派好谁为先锋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁为中军 谁为后应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公从不打无准备之仗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以往出征
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是先分派好谁为先锋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁为中军 谁为后应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这回打陶谦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么说打就打了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是因为这回与以往不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是要为父复仇 怒火满腔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已经乱了方寸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恨不能朝发夕至
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我的五万大军全都是先锋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们要一鼓作气拿下徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以免迟则生变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍 袁术等诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在接到主公哀疏的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很可能也会接到陶谦的求援书信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就袁绍的心性而言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他要犹豫几天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿不定主意是帮助陶谦好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是保持中立
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就在他犹豫这几天里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们一定要拿下徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}造成既成事实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你听听 荀彧说得多好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比我自个儿说得都好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不能和主公相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是跟着主公时间长了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多学了一些教益
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧 你是怕我嫉妒你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可以告诉你 不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我了解你的忠心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要是嫉妒你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不就是嫉妒我自个儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公的一席话 真是令人陶醉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹孟德亲率大军征讨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:14:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦自知不敌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只得出城乞罪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}汝何罪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹老太爷路经徐州时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想借此机会结交你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我们全家老少像伺候王公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦不不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像伺候自己的父亲那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伺候曹老太爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}临行时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我赠送了价值十万钱的礼品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并派部将张铠护送
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万不料此人恶行未改
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杀害了曹老太爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}使我铸成了大错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陷我于无义之绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因此我们全家老少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和徐州城的老少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都在为曹老太爷服孝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}启禀曹公
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我陶谦虽然身患重病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍要前往五凤山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}捉拿恶贼张铠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}亲手交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把他剐心取肝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}祭奠曹老太爷的在天之灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说得好听
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杀父之仇 不共戴天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}区区一个张铠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能让我父复活么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下虽然有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但出于有意献宠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无心获罪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乞求曹公看在这一节上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍恕我罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暂且退兵 容我杀贼自赎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了 从今年起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州府愿意每年向贵部提供
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二十万粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是想收买我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不不 我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不仅纵使部下杀害我父
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还暗中勾结袁绍 谋我兖州
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妄想与他人共分我的属地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹孟德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}世人皆知我陶谦向无大志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只图自保
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我何曾贪恋过别人的城池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你瞒得了别人瞒不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你一向都是故做韬晦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虚伪 险恶 我跟你明说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看在你披麻戴孝的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日我就不杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赶紧回去备战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}两日之后我要拿下徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹孟德 我陶谦也是一方刺史
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身受皇命 世受国恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实我比你父亲还大一岁哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我卑躬屈膝的向你乞罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都乞到这个地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还不放过我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你非要强占徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非要逼我徐州数十万军民
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以死相杭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}两日之后破城
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要取你的首级祭奠家父
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阁下如果知趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回家洗净了脖子等着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}转告徐州城中的百姓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}破城之后 我不会屠城
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}凡为我父服丧者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都可以免死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公你为何不下令趁势攻城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不是让我们一鼓作气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿下徐州吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我发现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦比我想象中的要厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我刚才仔细看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然他的城关遍插白旗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是每一杆白旗下头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都暗藏着强弓硬弩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看他表面上对我卑躬屈膝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实则故做韬晦 暗藏杀机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们一定做好了守城的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且城里的军民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也一定会跟他共存亡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦再是顽杭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过是八千守军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们五万精甲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂能拿它不下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他除了八千守军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有几十万百姓哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦素以仁爱治民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大难临头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}百姓们多会效命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你再看他的城关
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}高三丈有余 坚固无比
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们的人虽多 但多是轻骑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果强攻 势必伤亡太大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我答应给他们两天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是迫不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我们攻城的器械
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要两天之后才能到达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时再攻就可一鼓作气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:19:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将其拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传命下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就说陶谦已经吓得肝胆都破碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们一战可胜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让将士们歇息两天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三天日出时分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各部合力攻城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陪我喝杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶公子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶使君写给我家主公的信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公已经详细地阅过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁将军何时发兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么 发兵 不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公考虑再三
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是不能发兵相救
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在你来冀州求救之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹操的哀疏已经到了冀州
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}疏上写得分明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这杀父之仇可是不共戴天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公若是在此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又为此事而发兵相救
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不仅难于服众
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实在是出师无名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我父亲从未纵使张铠杀害曹嵩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相反 他之所以派人去护送曹嵩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他是想结交曹操啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这正是这件事情的可笑可悲之处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你父陶谦原本是想向那曹操献媚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不料想弄巧成拙 画虎没成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反类其犬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}致使你们两家反目成仇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:21:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兵戎相见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:22:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可悲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}堂堂的朝廷命官
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一州之长尊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}居然做出了这种荒唐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恕许攸直言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这件事情实在是愚蠢之极
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶公子不妨想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公袁绍袁本初
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是何许人也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乃四世三公
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}声振寰宇 威名满天下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公总不能在你父陶谦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做出了这等可笑可悲的事之后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再荒唐的添上一些可叹和可怜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恕不远送
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.74,0:23:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冀州袁绍不肯发兵相助
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}南阳袁术虽然肯发兵拒曹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.41,0:23:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但他却让家父割让武宁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}泗水两郡之地作为酬谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二袁原本与家父相交最深
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但在紧要关头却都婉言推辞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公孙将军 家父的生死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和徐州城五十三万百姓的存亡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就仰仗将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操一旦得了徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必然会图谋中原
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}进而会与袁氏二雄争天下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}侄儿猜想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍和袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都知道曹操得势之后的后果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但这两兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.21,0:23:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}本来就是面和心不和
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.88,0:23:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都想等着对方先发兵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自己坐观成败
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以取渔翁之利呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.02,0:23:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这对儿堂兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.62,0:23:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可谓是一对儿笑面虎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.22,0:23:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}两头乌角鲨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}两人之间早晚必有一场恶斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.43,0:23:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公孙将军 我求你快快发兵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.73,0:24:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}救救徐州城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报 禀主公
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.44,0:24:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}平原令刘备求见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.74,0:24:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德老弟来了 陶侄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你且下去歇息
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.74,0:24:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待我和玄德商议之后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.64,0:24:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再做定夺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.71,0:24:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.72,0:24:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.12,0:24:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备拜见公孙将军
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.72,0:24:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贤弟啊 你且看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.53,0:24:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦发给我的求援信
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.93,0:24:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操亲率五万大军攻打徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.73,0:24:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦危在旦夕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.94,0:24:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老弟呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.04,0:24:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说我是救陶谦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.44,0:24:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是不救哇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.45,0:24:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敢问将军的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.22,0:24:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是想救陶谦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.92,0:24:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我现在是兵少将弱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.72,0:24:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非曹操之对手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.72,0:24:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说了袁绍和袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.43,0:25:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各自有二十多万兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.23,0:25:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却坐观成败
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.93,0:25:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我哪有能力救徐州哇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.13,0:25:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即便是我全军出援
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.24,0:25:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且侥幸成功了 我得到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.74,0:25:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只不过是得到像陶谦这般弱友
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.54,0:25:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却结下了像曹操袁绍这样的强敌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.45,0:25:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不值啊 不智啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.52,0:25:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军所言 在下万万不敢苟同
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.02,0:25:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶恭祖为先帝钦命 忠义厚道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.52,0:25:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}治徐州多年 贤名远播
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.63,0:25:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹孟德以报父仇为名 趁火打劫
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.93,0:25:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}图谋徐州六郡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.93,0:25:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽说是乱世争雄各凭实力
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.84,0:25:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我总觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.84,0:25:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最终必定是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.14,0:25:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得人心者方能得天下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.64,0:25:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下此次前来就是来和将军辞行的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.75,0:25:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要去徐州 援救陶谦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.42,0:26:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说刘备啊 你才有多少兵马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.22,0:26:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}区区两三千人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.92,0:26:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟敢去破曹操的五万大军
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.23,0:26:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这可是以卵击石哟
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.83,0:26:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我刘备未必是卵
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.03,0:26:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他曹操也未必就是石头
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.74,0:26:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也罢 既然你非得要去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.74,0:26:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我就借给你精兵三千
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.34,0:26:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍壮声势
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.35,0:26:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢公孙将军
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.95,0:26:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下不要将军任何兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.02,0:26:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只向将军借一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.62,0:26:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}借谁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.53,0:26:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}常山赵子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.93,0:26:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你为何独独要借赵云
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.84,0:26:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}世人只知道吕布名冠天下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.44,0:26:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却并不知道赵子龙之勇
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.14,0:27:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}远胜于匹夫吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.15,0:27:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}子龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.95,0:27:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.95,0:27:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你愿意跟随刘备去援救徐州吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.72,0:27:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将愿往
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.23,0:27:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.73,0:27:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们两个啊是英雄相惜
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.63,0:27:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 子龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.94,0:27:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你就随刘备去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.94,0:27:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢将军
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.54,0:27:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢将军
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.95,0:27:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公孙将军虽有数万将士
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.45,0:27:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但真正的英雄只有子龙一个
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.95,0:27:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实在下对玄德君的人品
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.95,0:27:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早已是仰慕已久 从今以后
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.26,0:27:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要主公一声令下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.22,0:27:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下赴汤蹈火在所不辞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.93,0:27:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 子龙 从此
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.13,0:27:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘关张赵就是四兄弟了 你意如何
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.03,0:27:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢主公大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.43,0:27:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.93,0:27:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们赶紧赶回平原县
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.54,0:27:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日一早奔赴徐州 我估计
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.64,0:28:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦支持不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.34,0:28:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只怕三五日之内便会破城
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.04,0:28:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命 在下有一事不解
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.25,0:28:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.35,0:28:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍袁术坐拥几十万大军
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.65,0:28:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却彼此观望
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.95,0:28:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不肯发兵援救徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.05,0:28:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公兵不过两千
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.06,0:28:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将不过关 张 赵
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.86,0:28:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却何以敢对杭曹操呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.03,0:28:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 问得好 子龙若不问
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.23,0:28:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我早晚也会告诉你 方今天下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.23,0:28:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各路英雄豪杰
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.33,0:28:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皆以兵马权谋称霸一方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.74,0:28:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而我刘备在兵马上远不如他们
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.54,0:28:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我有两样 是他们没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.84,0:28:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其一 我以仁义为立身之本
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.44,0:28:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待人之道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.54,0:28:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为天下大乱首先在于人心丧乱
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.35,0:28:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欲治乱世必先收人心
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.95,0:28:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我必须以仁抗不仁 以义拒不义
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.25,0:28:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其二 我身为汉皇后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.76,0:28:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}除贼扶汉是我毕生心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.06,0:28:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那陶谦是先帝钦命 素以仁义治政
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.33,0:28:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我助他便是扶汉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.93,0:29:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而曹操名为报父仇 实为取徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.24,0:29:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}意在取天下 耿耿野心 路人皆知
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.24,0:29:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我举兵杭曹 便是以仁抗不仁
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.04,0:29:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以天下大义拒袅雄之不义
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.25,0:29:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算此战不胜
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.75,0:29:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}世人也能看见一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.75,0:29:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何事
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.55,0:29:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正道不灭 大义永存
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.64,0:29:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 探马来报
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.84,0:29:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍 袁术 刘表
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.65,0:29:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公孙瓒等各路诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.35,0:29:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都不愿意出兵援助陶谦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.05,0:29:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然不出我之所料
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.95,0:29:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有人愿意为了一个陶谦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.76,0:29:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟我为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.16,0:30:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州是我们的囊中之物了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.33,0:30:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.23,0:30:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}攻城的器械大部分也到位了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.34,0:30:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日中午 开始攻城
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.54,0:30:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有一件事令在下不安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.74,0:30:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.35,0:30:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兖州城来信
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.25,0:30:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说南郊一带发现吕布的兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.05,0:30:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}八千至一万
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.55,0:30:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}似有所图谋
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.85,0:30:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布 败军之将 丧主之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.96,0:30:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不足为虑
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.43,0:30:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道他敢攻我的兖州大营
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.83,0:30:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公善用兵者 不虑胜先虑败
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.34,0:30:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万一吕布作乱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.74,0:30:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兖州可是我们的大本营啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.85,0:30:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可是把精兵强将
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.55,0:30:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都带来打徐州了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.95,0:31:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兖州几乎是座空城
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.15,0:31:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 吕布可是骁勇异常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.26,0:31:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布虽勇
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.66,0:31:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贪而好利 勇而无谋
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.16,0:31:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连袁绍 袁术都不敢动我的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.26,0:31:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兖州大营 他敢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.43,0:31:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.64,0:31:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我估计三日之内
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.34,0:31:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就能攻下徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.94,0:31:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}城一破
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.34,0:31:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就令许褚带领两万精兵
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.44,0:31:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回防兖州大营
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.05,0:31:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许褚早就想跟吕布大战三百合了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.05,0:31:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从地图上看 主公的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.16,0:31:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}似乎已超出了徐州啦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.96,0:31:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.36,0:31:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下有那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.96,0:31:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我惦记着它们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.67,0:32:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}停
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.77,0:32:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待我让那陶谦老儿 出城受降
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.56,0:32:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.66,0:32:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 陶谦拒降
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.57,0:32:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公有令 立即攻城
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.37,0:33:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杀 杀 杀
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.75,0:33:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}点火 放
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.95,0:33:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}弓弩阵 放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.01,0:33:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 有兵马前来援助陶谦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.55,0:33:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是袁绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.55,0:33:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.75,0:33:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.84,0:34:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.35,0:34:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那会是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.45,0:34:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来将何人 报上姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.05,0:34:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我乃常山赵子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.77,0:35:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我原本以为
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.57,0:35:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布已经天下无敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.08,0:35:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没想到有人比他还勇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.28,0:35:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是谁的部将
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.25,0:35:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 他们打的平原令的旗号
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.05,0:36:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来此人是刘备的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.15,0:36:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备 他只有区区几千人马
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.16,0:36:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也敢来与我为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.06,0:36:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的 他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.47,0:36:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.37,0:36:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.88,0:36:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 这是谁的兵马 来援啦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.88,0:36:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看旗号 好像是平原令刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.55,0:36:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.97,0:36:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}狂贼 胆大包天
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.87,0:36:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公不可轻敌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.88,0:36:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备既来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.18,0:36:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必有准备
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.98,0:37:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽 张飞已经得了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.58,0:37:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在又多出了这么一员猛将
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.28,0:37:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备这厮 为何如此命好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.59,0:38:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 是否继续攻城
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.56,0:38:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.36,0:38:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.16,0:38:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传命 缓缓退军 引他们来攻
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.96,0:38:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.57,0:38:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公有令缓缓退军
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.17,0:38:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撤退 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.15,0:38:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操大军压境之际
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.18,0:38:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州生死关头
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.49,0:38:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我陶谦遍求各镇诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.16,0:38:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而他们虽然坐拥数十万兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.46,0:38:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却无一肯发兵相救
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.06,0:39:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.17,0:39:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我井没有求他 他却仗义前来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.77,0:39:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以区区两千兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.47,0:39:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却能冲破曹军铁桶般的阵势
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.47,0:39:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却能冲破曹军铁桶般的阵势
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.88,0:39:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}解徐州大难哪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.28,0:39:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德呀
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.78,0:39:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老夫我感激之情无以言表哇
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.69,0:39:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶公 刘备早就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.06,0:39:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下之大唯徐州太守陶恭祖
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.26,0:39:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最是宽仁厚道 爱民如子
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.47,0:39:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备想
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.17,0:39:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果连陶恭祖这样的仁德之君
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.07,0:39:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都无法生存的话
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.48,0:39:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么这个国家还有什么指望
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.48,0:39:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大汉何日才可中兴
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.98,0:39:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备无尺寸功德 惟有忠勇二字
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.89,0:39:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日我相救徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.29,0:40:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}便是救世道良心
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.56,0:40:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}救我大汉天下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.16,0:40:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说得好啊 请 尽饮此盅
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.67,0:40:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谨以此酒 敬陶前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.68,0:40:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请 请
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.68,0:40:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道我自己德薄力弱
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.68,0:40:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无福提领徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.29,0:40:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而今天下纷乱 纲常崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.99,0:40:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能匡扶汉室者
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.59,0:40:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非你这样的英雄不可呀
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.36,0:40:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.57,0:40:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.37,0:40:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就把徐州五十万百姓
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.47,0:40:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}托附给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.77,0:40:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日我就上奏朝廷
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.18,0:40:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敕你为徐州牧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.28,0:41:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万万不可 刘备万万不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.39,0:41:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有何不可呀
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.69,0:41:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连曹操那样的奸雄都能窃取兖州
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.89,0:41:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你身为汉帝宗室
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.89,0:41:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}德行操守皆具王室的风范
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.66,0:41:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何就不能统领徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.97,0:41:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不是曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.97,0:41:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下此行前来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.77,0:41:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是为了救徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.77,0:41:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而不是为了图谋徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.98,0:41:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶公请万万不可陷我于不义
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.88,0:41:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德啊 请为徐州百姓着想
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.19,0:41:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}担此重任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.00,0:41:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀陶公
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.27,0:41:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备今日留言在此
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.77,0:41:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一旦曹操退兵 徐州转危为安
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.77,0:41:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下即行离去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.57,0:41:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重归平原县
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.68,0:42:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德呀 真是令人敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.89,0:42:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此事咱们以后从长计议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.89,0:42:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哥啊 你这个人啊是样样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.70,0:42:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是有桩毛病不好
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.37,0:42:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪桩毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.57,0:42:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心善 善得太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.27,0:42:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心善也是毛病吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.38,0:42:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.18,0:42:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人家陶谦大好的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.08,0:42:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}送你一座徐州城
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.38,0:42:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你为何不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.08,0:42:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这徐州落在咱手里
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.88,0:42:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总比落在曹操手里强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.29,0:42:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二哥 你说是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.49,0:42:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟所言并非没有道理呀
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.19,0:42:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们这三兄弟自桃园结义以来
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.60,0:42:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直飘泊不定 如果得了徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.00,0:42:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就有了一座坚城立足
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.97,0:42:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}进可以图大业 退可以保平安
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.87,0:43:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}住嘴 你们俩听着 再说此话
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.68,0:43:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就不敢认你们为兄弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.08,0:43:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我刘备宁肯粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.98,0:43:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也绝不行此不义
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.19,0:43:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好好好 哥哥不让说
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.19,0:43:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那咱就把嘴给缝上
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.99,0:43:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}城池算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.60,0:43:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是兄弟要紧 二哥 你说是不是
